# 💼 Enterprise Expense Management System - Frontend

This is the **frontend** of our group project: **Enterprise Expense Management System**. This system helps organizations manage employee expenses, reimbursements, and approvals efficiently.

---

## 🚀 Project Overview

The project is designed to provide a complete solution for managing, tracking, and analyzing business expenses. It includes:

- 🧑‍💼 Role-based access (Employee, Manager, Admin)
- 🧾 Expense submission and file uploads
- ✅ Approval and reimbursement tracking
- 📊 Real-time analytics and dashboard
- 📂 Report generation

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

| Layer      | Technology             |
|------------|------------------------|
| Frontend   | React.js               |
| State Mgmt | Redux (optional)       |
| Styling    | CSS / Tailwind / MUI   |
| Routing    | React Router           |
| Charts     | Chart.js / Recharts    |
| Alerts     | React Toastify         |
| HTTP       | Axios                  |

---

## 📁 Folder Structure

src/ ├── components/ # Reusable UI components (form, charts, cards, etc.) ├── pages/ # Different route pages (Login, Dashboard, ExpenseList) ├── services/ # Axios API calls ├── redux/ # Global state management ├── assets/ # Images, icons, and logos ├── App.js # Main app config with routes └── index.js # Entry point


---

## 🧩 Core Components

### 1. Authentication & Users
- `LoginForm`
- `RegisterForm`
- `UserProfile`
- `RoleBasedAccess`

### 2. Expense Management
- `ExpenseForm`
- `ExpenseList`
- `ExpenseItem`
- `FileUpload`
- `CategoryFilter`

### 3. Approval Workflow
- `PendingApprovals`
- `ApprovalCard`
- `ApprovalHistory`

### 4. Analytics & Reports
- `DashboardOverview`
- `ExpenseChart`
- `CategoryPieChart`
- `ReportDownload`

### 5. UI Elements
- `Navbar`, `Sidebar`, `Footer`
- `Loader`, `ToastAlerts`, `ProtectedRoute`

---

## 🔐 Roles and Permissions

| Role     | Permissions                                           |
|----------|--------------------------------------------------------|
| Employee | Submit expenses, view status                          |
| Manager  | View team expenses, approve/reject                    |
| Admin    | Manage users, categories, view reports, audit logs    |

